tr.td:
Test foods made up of traditional plants such as:
Whole wheat (belila 1);
Partially decorticated wheat (belila 2);
Fenugreek powder seeds;
Germinated fenugreek seeds;
Edible lupine
Roasted chickpea;
Biscuit 1 (made from baked whole grain wheat and powdered fenugreek);
Biscuit 2 (made from whole grain wheat and milled chickpea)
